snippet.title: HUGE MAKEUP COLLECTION DECLUTTER! - FOUNDATIONS, CONCEALERS, POWDERS & MORE | AMBER HOWE
snippet.description:
Hey Babes!

Im back with another declutter!

What better a time to sort out and declutter my collection. Today we are going to be decluttering my top two makeup drawers which includes my foundation, concealer, setting sprays, primer, blushers, bronzer, highlighters & powders.
*
*
Come join my family - hit that subscribe button:
https://www.youtube.com/c/AmberHowexox

Instagram - amberhowexox - https://www.instagram.com/amberhowexox/?hl=en

Facebook – https://www.facebook.com/AmberHowexox/
Blog - www.amberhowe.co.uk
